Class LongRunningRecognizeResponse.Builder 

public static final class LongRunningRecognizeResponse.Builder extends GeneratedMessageV3.Builder<LongRunningRecognizeResponse.Builder> implements LongRunningRecognizeResponseOrBuilder
The only message returned to the client by the `LongRunningRecognize` method.
 It contains the result as zero or more sequential `SpeechRecognitionResult`
 messages. It is included in the `result.response` field of the `Operation`
 returned by the `GetOperation` call of the `google::longrunning::Operations`
 service.

Protobuf type google.cloud.speech.v1.LongRunningRecognizeResponse
